Cell["\<\
Then \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]un-preparing\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] of auxiliary \
state is performed as preparation in reverse, with effects at the end in \
practice implemented as measurements with post-selection:\
\>", "Text",
